com.app.utility.validation

Class BootstrapValidationTool

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.app.utility.validation.BootstrapValidationTool

  •  class BootstrapValidationTool
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains all the validation logic that validates EACH row of data in the List returned by OpenCSV tool. A BootstrapValidator is required to be instantiated to make use of this class.
